# Express Server
## Set Up and Run:
In the server directory:
```
    npm install
```

Config File - config.env

MONGO_DB_URL : set this to the url to your mongo database 
JWT_SECRET : a jwt secret used for authenication

To generate run the following command and copy the value and place it in the config.env: 

```
node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(32).toString('hex'))"

```

Then to start the server:
```
    npm start
```
This will start the server running at http://localhost:3000/

# React/Vite Client

## Set Up and Run 

In the client directory:

```
    npm install
```

Then to start the client:
```
    npm run dev
```
This will start the client here: http://localhost:5173/ 